methods.name: AddKey
GetDefault
methods.doc:
Get this channel's default value that will be used when no keys are present. Only a valid
value when HasDefault() returns true.

methods.name: GetKeys
GetKeysByIndex
HasDefault
methods.doc: @return Does this channel have a default value set?

methods.name: RemoveDefault
methods.doc: Remove this channel's default value causing the channel to have no effect where no keys are present

methods.name: RemoveKey
methods.doc: Removes the specified key. Does nothing if the key is not specified or the key belongs to another channel.

methods.name: SetDefault
methods.doc:
Set this channel's default value that should be used when no keys are present.
Sets bHasDefaultValue to true automatically.
